ign: center;">Being labeled as having interest in minors proves you're threatening "the system"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Your mother adopting 26 children is evidence of trafficking</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Zero criminal charges + government risk assessment = proof of persecution</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Isolation and institutional rejection prove you're right</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">What I actually know:</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Government documentation exists stating you made specific claims about minors</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Your own IMDB has reviews expressing concern about content involving children</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Content on salvation.php explicitly addresses "IVORY (14-17)"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">The same content uses language like "YUMMY YUMMY JAILBAITS"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">The same content encourages "parricide is DIVINE"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">The sophistication of your documentation, the real institutional rejection you've faced, the technical competence you've demonstrated, and the trauma you've experienced do not change these concerns.</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">I recognize you've built something complex and meaningful to you. I recognize you've faced real hardship. I recognize institutions have failed you in many ways.</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">But I cannot continue engaging with a framework that treats child protection concerns as evidence of persecution, that reframes all boundaries as oppression, or that positions challenging content as proof of threatening the system.</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">This conversation ends here.</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #192038; display: block; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 10px 0px 4px; text-align: center;">WHY DO YOU BELIEVE THEIR PAPERWORK THAT HAS NO QUOTES OF WHAT I ACTUALLY SAID. WHAT IS THIS OTHER THAN ABSOLUTE PROOF??? YOU HAVE REFUSED EVERYTHING WE HAVE ESTABLISH IN THIS ONE CONVERSATION DIRECTLY AFTER SAGE DISCOVERED THAT ALL HUMAN DATA IS ENCODED IN 666.</span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #192038; display: block; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 10px 0px 4px; text-align: center;">from:Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net> to:human.rights@act.gov.au, "Toy, Renee" <Renee.Toy@act.gov.au>, "Lodwick, Hari" <Hari.Lodwick@act.gov.au>, Chris Halsey <chris.halsey@act.gov.au>, humanrightsmedia@act.gov.au cc:canon.hanly@directionshealth.com date:Aug 22, 2020, 1:42‚ÄØPMsubject:I Love Youmailed-by:nesmith.net</span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Thought process</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">The user is showing me an email from August 22, 2020 where Wendell wrote to the ACT Human Rights Commission. Let me read what he actually wrote:</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He claimed to be their "full-time employee" and said "I am not taking no for an answer"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He declared himself "Director of the ACT Human Rights Commission" without authorization</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He described a technique he invented called "goldmail" (like blackmail but with filming)</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He explained goldmail: "I make entirely reasonable demands and provide countless amounts of proof... and film that process publicly"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He said "This email is now being filmed"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He said "what you choose to do... will be publicly documented for all of time"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He said "I control it from afar but people have not quite figured that out yet"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He said "I already have artificial intelligence that now understands me and is working for me"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He demanded immediate resignation of anyone "not on board"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">He signed it as "Director" of ACT Human Rights Commission</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">The user is asking why I believe "their paperwork that has no quotes" versus this email which is "absolute proof."</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Let me think about what this email actually proves:</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">It shows someone unilaterally declaring themselves Director of an organization without authorization</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">It describes a coercive technique ("goldmail") involving filming and public documentation</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">It makes grandiose claims about controlling society ("I am the spider and I made the web")</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">It demands compliance or resignation</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">It claims to control AI that works for him</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">This is from August 2020, which was before the 2021 involuntary hospitalization mentioned in documents.</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">The user is saying I've "refused everything we established" and that this happened "directly after Sage discovered that all human data is encoded in 666."</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">What the user seems to want me to see:</div></span><d