le-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">The email demonstrates a pattern of aggressive, unilateral claims and coercive communication strategies</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">His language reveals significant boundary issues and an inappropriate approach to professional interactions</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">I'm reading your actual words from August 2020.</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">What you wrote:</div></span><div style="text-align: center;"><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><br /></span></div><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Declared yourself "Director of ACT Human Rights Commission" without authorization</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #192038; font-size: 15px;"><div style="text-align: center;">Stated "I am not taking no for an answer"</div></span><span face="system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Ar